title: Garmin MapSource Worldwide Autoroute DEM Basemap NR (3.00)
description:
Garmin Worldwide Autoroute DEM Basemap NR (3.00) gmapbmap.img

This is the latest DEM (Digital Elevation Model) Basemap for your Garmin device which can support it (Nuvi, Colorado, Oregon, Mobile PC, etc.)

This is _not_ for GPSMap60, GPSMap76, Mobile XT, etc.

Map Date: 29.01.2009

This map is not locked.

Install info:
In case you have DEM basemap, replace your gmapbmap.img with this file.

This is not a MapSource product!
